column2: mein ne dekhi hai original punjabi movie maula jatt jo kay bilkul jahil type kay gaaon kay 2 logon maula jatt ( hero ) and noori natt ( villain ) ki apas mein larayee jhagron se bherpoor kahani . iss movie ki interesting baat iss kay dialogues & amp ; sultan rahi & amp ; mustafa qureshi ki achi acting thi . wesay thi to ye serious action movie lekin mera iss movie kay zyada ter scenes ko dekh ker hans hans ker bura haal hogaya thaa . iss movie mein bohot saray famous dialogues hain jesay…chuk lo ( utha lo ) … . nawa aayan ein sonriyan ( naye aye ho pyaray ) … . totay totay kerdeiyan gaa ( tukray tukray kerdoon gaa ) …hor maar sonriyan ( aur maaro pyare )... aj de baad jaddon we teri wesaakhi zameen te wajjay gi te uddon thak thak thak di awaz nayen noori natt natt natt de awaz ayegi ( aak kay baad jab bhi teri besaakhi zameen se takraye gi tou uss mein se thak thak thak ki nahin noori natt natt natt ki awaz ayegi ). ab dekhtay hain kay iss movie ka remake kesa banta hai & amp ; mummy daddy type kay actors fawad khan & amp ; hamza ali abbasi maula jatt and noori natt kay roles mein kiss tarah fit hotay hain . aasia chakori & amp ; aaliya kay roles mein kaun kaun si actresses ko sign kiya jata hai . maza ayega dekh ker iss new version ko .

column2: Phone tou no doubt bohat smart hai, looks mein bhee pyara aur qeemat mein bhee bohat zyada nai hai, tou aik achi choice hai kharedari ki. Is ka camera price kay hisab se bohat acha hai, light mein ya dark mein, picture quality bohat achee aatee hai, aur battery bhee lagbag aik din poora nikla letee hai. System ka istemal bhee mezay ka hai, android OS chalanay mein koi masla nai karta, lekin 1 GB ram honay ki waja se kabhi kabar mushkilat paish aatay hain. Jaisay mein social media bohat use karta hoon tou saray caches ram pe bhari parh jatay hain aur ram perform nai kartee, phone lag hona shuruh krdetee hai. Kbahi contacts mein scroll kartay waqt phone hang hojata hai aur number dial krne kay 30 seconds baad pata chalta hai kay call lag gayee hai ya nai, jab kay phone bohat lag krta hai. Lekin lagging kay elawa, budget mien yeh phone bohat acha hai, nbas mein yehee recommend karoonga kay iskay naye model mein ram ki behtari karein. 1GB ab kaun use karta hai?

column2: assalamoaleikom ... awam ka ghussa kion berhta hi ja raha hai ? tu arz hai k insaan k kirdar aur ikhlaak ka sab se barra dushman uss ka nafs aur bhook hai ... in do ki azmaesh mein jo pora utra jeet ussi ki hai jab hr ummed toot jaee taleem khandan izzate nafs digree personality kabliyat hote hue b haram k maal pe palne waloon ko sifarish pe bherti kr k haq talfi ki jaee jab ghr k masaeil bachoon ki hasrat bharri aankhein un ka mustakbil daoo pe laga ho . jab aankhoon k samne aziz rishtedar tarap kr mout ko galle laga lein magr ghalat medicine supplyers ko koi na pooche . jab jawan ghr bethi behnoo ko berozgaar bhai baap un ko borha hote dekhein jahan eik engnering ki taleem hasil kr k pakore bechne ki nobat aa jaee . jahan maoon k lakhte jiger aghwah k baad laash ki soorat walden ko wapis milein aur kidnapers ko koi phansi pe na latkaee . jab paisa eik makhsoos tabke k hath lag jaee jab ghareeb ko ata daal chawal khoone jiger de kr b 2 waqt ki roti ki soorat na mile jab taleem ka shouk rakhne wale bijli ki wajah se roshni se mehroom hn jab ghareeb mazdoor ko din bher ki kamaee bhata khoor kafroon ko deni per jaee jahan eik mobile k badle gumrah nojawan logon ki jaan le lein jahan awam ki hifazat krne wale bahu betion ki asmatoon k qatil hoon jahan eik makhsoos jahil aur kam aqal tabka apni aamarat aur bahir k paise ka dhandora pite jahan awam ko nazar andaaz kr k gumrah aurtein merd assembly mein qeemti libaas makeup aur caroon ki numaesh kr k dawtein urate hue serkari kherche pe rang barangi mumalik ki seer karein jahan khwaboon mein khud ko makbool leader samajh k ghantooon trafikk rok kr kitne begunahon ki jaan li jaee aur kitnoo ko imtehanoo se late kerwa k un ka mustakbil tareek kia jaee jahan tv studios mein in bheekari politions k zaati shows aur gali galooch k siwa kuch na reh jae jahan islam ko dafan kr k new time new style pe awam ka khoon nichoor kr ayashi k adde chalaee jaein

column2: i guess sara aur alishba k comments ubi tuk yaad hain aap ko is leye saba hameed ki jaga saba qaamar likha gaya .... that show was really funny ... coming back to this episode i was just amazed and just when we were thinking that is it going further away ? they just brought us back with a bang ... every thing was realistic and just amazing to watch ... pool side scene was brillianty shot and acted except some mistakes like i don ' t know where he found a comb and when he took off that coat bcz i think he was wearing it when he left ... pareesa felt that she didn ' t need to tell him bcz i think she feels that now he will never be back and that is my concerned as well ... when he was crying un the pool i was thinking that k armaan k baap ne pareesa ko isi pool mein maara tha aur aaj armaan b maar gua pareesa k haathon ... i felt k armaan ki tkleef ub pareesa se b zyada ha and that is the best part about this drama i mean in how many dramas you see a man in a situation like this in which he gets to know that his father raped his wife ? i guess armaan sea view par hoga and she is going there ... and yes you are right about mahmood . he just wants to get away and i guess it ' s realistic bcz majority of people don ' t want to be punished for their sins so i guess it is more easy for the writer to punish mahmood bcz he isn ' t ashamed and i told you that asif raza mir said that this was the most difficult to choose and even his wife said that i don ' t like your role and i hate it so salute to asif raza mir sajab for doing this character ... mohsin and kubra are exceptional as always .... thanks for the wonderful review and it ' s always a cherry on a cake to read your reviews after watching an episode
